\lvert \cos z\rvert^2 = \lvert \cos x \cosh y - i\sin x \sinh y\rvert^2 = \cos^2 x\cosh^2 y + \sin^2 x\sinh^2 y = \cos^2 x + \sinh^2 y
\lvert \sin z\rvert^2 = \lvert \sin x\cosh y + i\cos x \sinh y\rvert^2 = \sin^2 x \cosh^2 y + \cos^2 x\sinh^2 y = \sin^2 x + \sinh^2 y
